{"tid":2109292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日外務省強硬派  垂秀夫傳接任駐中大使","createTime":"2020-07-15T06:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T08:07:35.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6df85c19d89c935455cb305e14b221233596b2b","tid":2109292,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T06:44:58.000Z","msg":"日本政府有意派遣外務省官房長垂秀夫擔任下任駐中國大使，現年59歲的垂秀夫被視為是外務省「中國班」裡少數對中強硬派，2013年擔任駐中公使任內，僅上任3個月即被緊急調回日本，外傳他被中國當局以「蒐集對中國不利情報」為由驅逐出境，垂秀夫深受首相安倍晉三信任，也曾於2016年被派駐備受矚目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3229172\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3229172&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu7JtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=b40460da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3229172&h=c361f3a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3229172</a>"},{"pid":"ecd621590f10917cf2617738ef78ed4bee2919b9","tid":2109292,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T08:07:35.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}